source.name: Washington Department of Fish and Wildlife Water Access Sites
source.description:
The WATER ACCESS SITES layer provides point location, administrative oversight information, disabled usability status, directions, special use issues, and general descriptive data for the Washington Department of Fish and Wildlife’s (WDFW) managed water access sites.

For more information see https://fortress.wa.gov/dfw/public/PublicDownload/wildlife/WaterAccessSites/WDFWWaterAccessSites.pdf
